- Codebase:
	- miniaudio.so?

- Modules:
	- fmsynth
		- Useful for creating samples:
			- initial phase offset
	- Compressor (ducking with named pipe)

- Sequencer:
	- Format: define commands (sounds) as characters, make text character grid of tracks and sounds

- Arguments:
	- Volume control for each module
	- Channel control for each module
	- Lifetime control for each module
	- FM Synth waveform specification
